<br />\n好多說話背後去到好深層次意義<br />\n我開始 take notes, 差不多每講一句我就記低<br />\n到好多年後d notes 有時都會攞翻出黎睇解答難題<br />\n上完十幾堂加上認真做功課<br />\n真係已經好過大部分 developers <br />\n<br />\n希望你學習順利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"多謝曬ching, 會努力研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971b54f62350cc3c15a3e4642f36e08916256b6d","tid":1142244,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"學下excel先"},{"pid":"fe4005a7ec8a829bde68f3f0dcc374b279d4683d","tid":1142244,"uid":208375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"934a14d95e29b8ed1c46942f8206080e2c377f1d","tid":1142244,"uid":36724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0358350509827715538dbbc3937231cf689bfdad","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afab57a1b6c474e6c794dd930cdab8cd61c0fd7e","tid":1142244,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\n<br />\n想學下big data/ data management 係咪而家通常python 學起?<br />\n利申識少少VBA, 都叫識普通programming logic"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"Python 係開始<br />\n不過唔好限制自己喺 Python 度，最終要玩埋 Java (big data) &amp; JavaScript (visualisation)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好, 咁由python 起步學下先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"巴打自學定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想學 但完全冇底<br />\n唔知點入手"},{"pid":"f632f23b5c94e27b672488a3bd504f893aedb8c9","tid":1142244,"uid":43314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"