:0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3schools.com%2F&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=0cafc3f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.w3schools.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8c88919f3fde215f04e574fd08cb39a6c6411a","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f632f23b5c94e27b672488a3bd504f893aedb8c9","tid":1142244,"uid":43314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"上網自學，如果學一排都覺得學唔識最好唔好做呢行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"係咪個底唔夠實？睇下 EdX CS50 同埋另外嗰位巴打介紹嘅 course 睇下有冇幫助<br />\n<br />\n或者玩下 leetcode，網上好多教學可參考答案<br />\n<br />\n又或者可以上黎 Tecky 傾下計，都係免費，我地開放課室，唔會鎖人，唔一定要報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲學生之前同你情況差唔多，傾下計都得"},{"pid":"024e5a47aa19f9c6329f6f22d34c8cab8c973286","tid":1142244,"uid":130565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"寫android 首先要學java<br />\n你唔識java 你睇人做你都係估估下"},{"pid":"2a932e0e702cf0ec03e2d49cca4ff2f18b5bf995","tid":1142244,"uid":220701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewiwOYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewiwOYb.jpg&h=db2b326f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e023e5ee118b348a0d40da0a6b75a9c256aefee1","tid":1142244,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣冇 program 底, 黎緊都諗住由工聯會<br />\n最低層再開始讀起<br />\n<br />\n記得好多年前自學過 dreamware 同 Ms Access<br />\n自己曾經整到過 asp 網頁, 對 Excel VBA 都識小小<br />\nGoogle script 又係識小小<br />\n<br />\n所以想的起心肝慢慢學 Javascript, pyton etc<br />\nlanguage,  目標係整到 Web App"},{"pid":"429d12e4e32bf1c05dfa65eeafed3162220a0032","tid":1142244,"uid":231933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c76757017b517b15df761f1130c5440dbb968167","tid":1142244,"uid":5540,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cd037c00a5056215aa064716c82db18de94dabde","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":4,"dislike":157,"score":-153,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"認真，Tecky Academy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較一下：<br />\n- 工聯會<br />\n好平，非常入門，但又拖得好慢咁教。你上晒啲堂都無辦法自己做到一隻 app<br />\n<br />\n- 乜乜works<br />\n同工聯會差唔多<br />\n<br />\n- CS Master<br />\n如果係學店嘅，多數係吹水堂，都唔敢認真教你 programming，仲衰過工聯會，有張沙紙，但你唔會學到野。如果係認真嘅 Taught Master，應該唔會收你<br />\n<br />\n- Online Tutorial<br />\n比起以上嘅 options 算係最有可能成功，但你要非常有恆心，同埋未必有人指引到你，有啲 course 仲教錯人，質素參差。好多時候卡住的話冇人會幫你。而且你仲要為自己定返個 learning plan。時間較長<br />\n<br />\n- Tecky Academy<br />\n我地成個 course 包咗你要知嘅 computer science theory，可以學到去 Full Stack React Redux TypeScript + Kotlin，同時有晒實際業界用緊嘅技術，有啲現實 projects 會俾你做，仲會幫你搵埋工。total cost 係貴啲同埋長啲時間 (full time 15 weeks)，但呢十五星期我地就一直在旁陪住你，有咩卡住即刻解答你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：Co-founder"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:29:58.000Z","msg":"ching 多謝你但搞到個post 似打手post 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為自己都係業餘性質去學同埋多ot, 最多都係得禮拜六日得閒可以學，平日未必可以regular 上堂，所以都係prefer 彈性d 既野，但都好多謝你咁詳細介紹！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"試下 <a href=\"https://www.codecademy.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.codecademy.com%2F&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=bd02a344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.codecademy.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n我用佢學緊 React 。免費和最重要你可以寫 Code 練習，由淺入深。"},{"pid":"b6de155e1b92db17ddcbb0ee7dee5b2df9320f32","tid":1142244,"uid":1333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a932e0e702cf0ec03e2d49cca4ff2f18b5bf995","tid":1142244,"uid":220701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewiwOYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewiwOYb.jpg&h=db2b326f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"Python算係易入手"},{"pid":"f5bbc5cf5f2f83b43bd31b176b3469da20d44e0c","tid":1142244,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd037c00a5056215aa064716c82db18de94dabde","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":4,"dislike":157,"score":-153,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"認真，Tecky Academy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較一下：<br />\n- 工聯會<br />\n好平，非常入門，但又拖得好慢咁教。你上晒啲堂都無辦法自己做到一隻 app<br />\n<br />\n- 乜乜works<br />\n同工聯會差唔多<br />\n<br />\n- CS Master<br />\n如果係學店嘅，多數係吹水堂，都唔敢認真教你 programming，仲衰過工聯會，有張沙紙，但你唔會學到野。如果係認真嘅 Taught Master，應該唔會收你<br />\n<br />\n- Online Tutorial<br />\n比起以上嘅 options 算係最有可能成功，但你要非常有恆心，同埋未必有人指引到你，有啲 course 仲教錯人，質素參差。好多時候卡住的話冇人會幫你。而且你仲要為自己定返個 learning plan。時間較長<br />\n<br />\n- Tecky Academy<br />\n我地成個 course 包咗你要知嘅 computer science theory，可以學到去 Full Stack React Redux TypeScript + Kotlin，同時有晒實際業界用緊嘅技術，有啲現實 projects 會俾你做，仲會幫你搵埋工。total cost 係貴啲同埋長啲時間 (full time 15 weeks)，但呢十五星期我地就一直在旁陪住你，有咩卡住即刻解答你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：Co-founder"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:16:42.000Z","msg":"軟件台88個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc620a91a8f71b20b93519d89a5190d2cd103417","tid":1142244,"uid":155732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"無programming底，寫咩app <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435be3655f26edf6b9807fe3c266997202370333","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"f5bbc5cf5f2f83b43bd31b176b3469da20d44e0c","tid":1142244,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd037c00a5056215aa064716c82db18de94dabde","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":4,"dislike":157,"score":-153,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"認真，Tecky Academy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較一下：<br />\n- 工聯會<br />\n好平，非常入門，但又拖得好慢咁教。你上晒啲堂都無辦法自己做到一隻 app<br />\n<br />\n- 乜乜works<br />\n同工聯會差唔多<br />\n<br />\n- CS Master<br />\n如果係學店嘅，多數係吹水堂，都唔敢認真教你 programming，仲衰過工聯會，有張沙紙，但你唔會學到野。如果係認真嘅 Taught Master，應該唔會收你<br />\n<br />\n- Online Tutorial<br />\n比起以上嘅 options 算係最有可能成功，但你要非常有恆心，同埋未必有人指引到你，有啲 course 仲教錯人，質素參差。好多時候卡住的話冇人會幫你。而且你仲要為自己定返個 learning plan。時間較長<br />\n<br />\n- Tecky Academy<br />\n我地成個 course 包咗你要知嘅 computer science theory，可以學到去 Full Stack React Redux TypeScript + Kotlin，同時有晒實際業界用緊嘅技術，有啲現實 projects 會俾你做，仲會幫你搵埋工。total cost 係貴啲同埋長啲時間 (full time 15 weeks)，但呢十五星期我地就一直在旁陪住你，有咩卡住即刻解答你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：Co-founder"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:16:42.000Z","msg":"軟件台88個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"唔緊要<br />\n只要知道自己係做緊正確嘅事情就可以<br />\n<br />\n前日岩岩第二期畢業了，有一個請咗第一期學生嘅僱主，專登黎畢業禮多人謝我地，因為我地真係培訓到岩業界用嘅人才，解決左佢公司燃眉之急<br />\n<br />\n又正如另一個 post ( <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/985244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/985244/page/1</a> ) 嘅免費中學生 Python + Smart City 比賽，104 個負評，但我地過去四個月真係做足四個共 16 小時嘅工作坊，搵咗做杜拜 smart city 嘅 expert 講點做真正 smart city，又有 kaggle top 1% 嘅 data scientist 教 coding，今日完滿地完成整個比賽，竟然有個小五生學晒我地教嘅野，成功用 puppeteer + app inventor 整左個 openrice + MTR scraper，好多家長同學生爭住多謝我地<br />\n<br />\n繼續做正確嘅事，做啱嘅好事，終有一日會有人明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec48e67156a46d120310c4731425d31d2a2ab96c","tid":1142244,"uid":143621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b77a03ad57d2289a0d2b7895e47b16a778dd2a4","tid":1142244,"uid":44071,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"我幾看前都係從無到有入手學寫 app <br />\n到今日已經職業寫 app 幾年出過唔少算唔錯嘅 app 了<br />\n<br />\n當初自學又好似你咁無從入手<br />\n揾書睇揾網學都係唔係太淺學完等於冇學就係太難睇完一頭霧水<br />\n作為新手當時無法理解 OO 概念<br />\n<br />\n結果俾我揾到 Standard online course CS193P<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/course/developing-ios-11-apps-with-swift/id1309275316?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fcourse%2Fdeveloping-ios-11-apps-with-swift%2Fid1309275316%3Fl%3Den&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=85df096a\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/course/developing-ios-11-apps-with-swift/id1309275316?l=en</a><br />\n有晒 lecture video, notes, 功課<br />\n我終於從當中完整掌握 MVC 概念<br />\n當年 prof 係 Paul Hegarty<br />\n曾經係 Next 時代同 Steve Job 共事過<br />\n有份創立 Objective C<br />\n上多幾堂發現個 prof 字字珠璣<br />\n好多說話背後去到好深層次意義<br />\n我開始 take notes, 差不多每講一句我就記低<br />\n到好多年後d notes 有時都會攞翻出黎睇解答難題<br />\n上完十幾堂加上認真做功課<br />\n真係已經好過大部分 developers <br />\n<br />\n希望你學習順利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T16:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb330c8bac5a4347ee18635a3f27ef9eecd19614","tid":1142244,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:44:07.000Z","msg":"個post咁撚傳銷feel, 講返技術野啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"decbc38248f047554e9deadbcf96ba789d4282b1","tid":1142244,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3917465e3c8543d5c9e35ea836f5d651f0bfea8c","tid":1142244,"uid":42217,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"cityu cs master"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"Dllm"},{"pid":"89ce9f76c21be980ad49cbdb34b12d087d1216bc","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"eb330c8bac5a4347ee18635a3f27ef9eecd19614","tid":1142244,"uid":42767,"like":1,"