ps://tecky.io/zh_Hant/blog/</a><br />\n最近拍左兩段 video 教大家 scraping，第三段加緊字幕:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SHzR-3kHdDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSHzR-3kHdDE&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=7f261683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SHzR-3kHdDE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D_J--VOZ8vg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD_J--VOZ8vg&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=6d566356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D_J--VOZ8vg</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T16:55:36.000Z","msg":"留名學scraping，自己宜家睇返freecodecamp啲course。同上youtube 睇video , 不過如果巴打你啲科可到cef 又好似bootcamp 咁我實報"},{"pid":"e52e21f8601accf758a130e89a8c7acbd83e7c6b","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fc9f09f49840ffb9d498164cf3745a6097b99a09","tid":1142244,"uid":56475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89ce9f76c21be980ad49cbdb34b12d087d1216bc","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"eb330c8bac5a4347ee18635a3f27ef9eecd19614","tid":1142244,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:44:07.000Z","msg":"個post咁撚傳銷feel, 講返技術野啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"技術野一樣有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地咁耐以黎寫過嘅 blog: <a href=\"https://tecky.io/zh_Hant/blog/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftecky.io%2Fzh_Hant%2Fblog%2F&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=b2fd4bc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tecky.io/zh_Hant/blog/</a><br />\n最近拍左兩段 video 教大家 scraping，第三段加緊字幕:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SHzR-3kHdDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSHzR-3kHdDE&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=7f261683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SHzR-3kHdDE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D_J--VOZ8vg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD_J--VOZ8vg&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=6d566356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D_J--VOZ8vg</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T16:55:36.000Z","msg":"留名學scraping，自己宜家睇返freecodecamp啲course。同上youtube 睇video , 不過如果巴打你啲科可到cef 又好似bootcamp 咁我實報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:37:28.000Z","msg":"CEF 規定要同一個 course 搞足兩年先會審批<br />\n<br />\n例如今日如果教緊 React 的話，兩年後都一樣要同樣教緊 React，再加埋大約一年時間審批，先有資格做 CEF 課程。咁到時又差唔多要轉教第二樣了，所以啲 CEF 課程多數係教舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcde056587b41ca19212b235a65c2e4880549bc","tid":1142244,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T12:17:49.000Z","msg":"咩programming language都可以自學的"},{"pid":"b0dd1cc7e6214c23e091f7c39784ff5043691aa5","tid":1142244,"uid":43602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"短期programming course其實有無認受性， 如果想轉行但無時間讀過degree或者HD"},{"pid":"73e6e304832d40b3625cafcb8afac6fedb2cfcb1","tid":1142244,"uid":121636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0dd1cc7e6214c23e091f7c39784ff5043691aa5","tid":1142244,"uid":43602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"短期programming course其實有無認受性， 如果想轉行但無時間讀過degree或者HD"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:59:02.000Z","msg":"公司得兩類<br />\n1）睇學歷：一定要你係 U Grad/IVE，咁你讀咩 course 都冇用<br />\n2）睇技術：其實你拎咩 cert /邊度 grad 都唔關事，一黎就同你做 technical test<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果你要入行，最好就係操好技術<br />\n不過嗰啲得十幾～三四十個鐘嘅短期 course 唔足以令你入到行"}]}